#-------------------------------------------------- 
#   COMPILATION INSTRUCTIONS
#-------------------------------------------------- 

1. Mount the /home/ directory to local machine:
     $sshfs gass:/project/gas_seepage/jportiz ~/mount_gas_seepage/
2. Compile with latexmk on remote:
    $latexmk -f howto 

3. Clean up files if needed on remote if needed:
    $latexmk -c
    (NOTE)
    the following may be better, as it also removes *pdf file:
    $latexmk -C
